{"tid":54570,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"三十幾歲港女第一次打工，做做下喊","createTime":"2016-12-25T15:55:12.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-26T01:54:44.000Z","uid":69810,"like":2,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ceb82440658c259b79ce3ee4c14c6c70a974ad55","tid":54570,"uid":69810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T15:55:12.000Z","msg":"是咁的，做緊某大型銀行分行，早兩個月有個三十幾歲濃妝港女黎左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係用好厚都遮唔到好老嗰款，三十幾歲先第一次打工學人開始做branch trainee<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n乜都唔識唔在講，成日暗示自己好疊水，公司派飯盒佢都話食唔慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲係老細面前話俾狗都唔食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我心諗呢條極品港女做乜尻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n終於早兩日，有個稍為麻煩少少嘅客黎拎錢，條港女係個客面前嗚哇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁喊撚左出黎，我睇到幾撚想笑，點知仲要執條八婆手尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想知再講<br />\n<br />\n利申，其實份工少少辛苦，但唔至於要喊下嘛，總行已經無咁chur<br />\n想笑佢廢青但諗真啲佢已經係廢中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50dd8c271ffcd80ca74a39e9c4e996ffb0fe158d","tid":54570,"uid":69810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T15:56:03.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"ba7c78aea82b2639bceb598b2f6649c1b7d2dd2a","tid":54570,"uid":46231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T15:56:28.000Z","msg":"無人想知 唔好再講"},{"pid":"318c83e5a858df84f1e7eb05c917249a2998f057","tid":54570,"uid":27719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T15:57:17.000Z","msg":"無人想知呀屌你老母臭閪<br />\n咪撚講呀<br />\n講左死全家"},{"pid":"5f65d554f7088b69fa6c8ff066a65db880a26941","tid":54570,"uid":23235,"like